==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Postage
<hw>Post"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The price established
by law to be paid for the conveyance of a letter or other mailable
matter by a public post.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Postage stamp</b></col>, <cd>a government stamp required
to be put upon articles sent by mail in payment of the postage, esp. an
adhesive stamp issued and sold for that purpose.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Postal</ent>⟦br⟧
